learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-18T11:37:37.555Z",maintainer-agent,"Ownership wording is history-derived: an assignee update is an assignment, while an explicit claim operation is a claim; ranking perspective should follow an explicit assignee unless caller identity is separately provided."
